<doc id="578927" wikidata="Q788151" url="?curid=578927" title="Autonomic ganglion">
<text>An autonomic ganglion is a cluster of nerve cell bodies (a ganglion) in the autonomic nervous system. The two types are the sympathetic ganglion and the parasympathetic ganglion.

== References ==</text><links>
