*The Human Stapler, a superhero who uses his hands to bind his victims (a member of The Interesting Four)
*Larry Rolans, the host of Larry&#x27;s Corner

=== Celebrity impersonations ===
*John DeLorean
*John Hinckley
*Noel Paul Stookey
*Pete Best
*William F. Buckley
*John Lennon

